{"word":"Reed","slug":"reed","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Reed</b> A water plant<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=19&verse=7'>Isa 19:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=35&verse=7'>Isa 35:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=51&verse=32'>Jer 51:32</a><br/> Used as a measuring device of six cubits<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=40&verse=8'>Eze 40:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=41&verse=8'>Eze 41:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=42&verse=19'>Eze 42:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=45&verse=1'>Eze 45:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=11&verse=1'>Rev 11:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=21&verse=16'>Rev 21:16</a><br/> Mockingly given to Jesus as a symbol of royalty<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=29'>Mat 27:29</a><br/> Jesus smitten with<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=30'>Mat 27:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=19'>Mar 15:19</a><br/> Figurative, of weakness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=14&verse=15'>1Ki 14:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=18&verse=21'>2Ki 18:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=36&verse=6'>Isa 36:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=42&verse=3'>Isa 42:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=29&verse=6'>Eze 29:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=11&verse=7'>Mat 11:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=12&verse=20'>Mat 12:20</a>"}]}